14:
Great work today, you guys!
Especially you, Feanie! The childcare
industry is going nuts for you!
18:
Ehehe, so I was the goodest girl,
right? Yippee!
21:
W-wait, are you the Feanie I've
heard so much about?!
23: P-please, I beg of you! H-help...
29:
So your own trauma is preventing
you from sleeping...
31:
Sadly, yes... Ever since I almost lost
my life in the Kaleidoscope, I can't
sleep without reliving that horrible
day...
34: Feanie, think you can help him out?
37:
Maybe... But we won't know until we
try...
41:
Good boy, big boy... Time to go to
bed...
44:
Warm and fluffy, soft and fuzzy... 
Lay down your weary head...
50:
Argh! Get back! Stay away from
meee!
56:
This is quite the conundrum... 
We'll have to try something else.
59:
Hmmm... He just needs a better
dream, right?
64:
Yeah, but that's easier said than
done.
68:
Um, what kind of dream would you
like to see instead?
71:
I-I mean, anything's better than the
nightmares...
73:
But if I had to pick, I'd say... it'd be
nice to have one where I could see
my mom...
74:
She didn't want me to become an
adventurer, and we had a big fight
before I left. 
That was the last time  I saw her.
85:
Let's make that dream come true!
Now... time to go to bed!
89:
Warm and fluffy, soft and fuzzy... 
A touching reunion ahead...
100:
Mm... No more... I couldn't eat
another bite...
113:
This drowsiness... I can't... fight it...
Urgh...
117:
Hey, guys! Just checking in since it's
been a while—
121:
What the heck?! Why's everyone
asleep?!
136:
Looks like you got to meet your
mama... That's good.
138:
It's okay. You're allowed to.
There's always room for dessert.
141:
I'm just glad you got to see
someone you miss so much. There,
there.
148:
Now this is a surprise. I had no idea
you could do something like that!
153:
Can you really allow others to
dream of whatever it is they desire?
157:
Well... They hafta fall asleep with me,
but...
160:
If someone really, REALLY wants to
see someone, they'll appear in their
dreams.
164: I see... That's really quite amazing.
169: No... It's not amazing at all...
172:
Everyone else gets to see the person
they miss, but...
174:
I've... never met my mama in any of
those dreams...
181:
Maybe somewhere deep, deep
down... I don't want to meet her.
183:
What if... I don't actually love her as
much as I think I do?
188:
I don't think that's the case, Feanie.
Don't worry, I'm sure we'll figure out
why you can't see her.
192:
Besides, how you feel is up to you.
No dreams or lack thereof can tell
you otherwise.
196:
Precisely. Everyone expresses their
feelings of yearning in different
ways.
215: Hehe... I love you all very, very much!
